high_descs: Turn around to face the table.
Pick up the butter knife on the table behind the salt shaker.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Use the knife to slice the apple in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the bottom drawer of the fridge, place the knife inside, and then close it.
Turn right and walk back to the sink.
Take a slice of apple out of the sink.
Turn left and walk back to the fridge.
Open the bottom drawer of the fridge and place the apple slice inside, close the drawer, wait 5 seconds then open the drawer and take the apple slice back out.
Turn around then turn left and walk across the room to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple slice inside next to the mug, and then close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold apple slice in the microwave next to the mug.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter.
Pick up a butter knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink.
Turn left and go to the refrigerator
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Take an apple slice from the sink.
Turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Put the apple slice in the refrigerator and take the apple slice out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the microwave
Put the apple slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled apple slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the left
Walk over to the table
Pick the knife up from the kitchen table
Carry the knife to the fridge
Open the door to the fridge
Place the knife in the fridge
Walk over to the kitchen sink
Grab half of the apple from the kitchen sink
Carry the apple to the fridge
Open the door to the fridge
Place the apple in the fridge
Walk to the stove and pick up the food and place it into the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting stuff away and preparing food

high_descs: Turn around and face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around to face the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into 3 pieces.
Step to the left to face the fridge.
Place the knife into the fridge on the top shelf on the left side.
Step to the right to face the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple in the sink.
Step to the left to face the fridge.
Cool the piece of apple in the fridge and remove it.
Turn to the right and cross the room to face the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the piece of apple inside.
anns.task_desc: To cut an apple into piece, cool it, and store it in the microwave.

high_descs: While facing the fridge turn around and face the green table.
Pick up the knife directly behind the salt shaker and between the potato and brown dish on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Slice the apple in the sink into slices.
Turn to your left and walk to the fridge while carrying the knife.
Open the fridge door and place the knife in front of the tomato on the top shelf with its blade pointing to the left.
Close the fridge door and walk to the sink.
Pick up a slice of the apple.
Turn to your left and carry the apple slice to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the apple slice at the left end of the knife and close the fridge door; after cooling, open the fridge door and pick up the apple slice, close the fridge door.
Turn to your right and walk to the stove.
Look up to the microwave oven over the stove, open the microwave door, place the apple slice in the microwave in front of the handle of the black mug, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple, refrigerate it, bring it to the microwave oven
